original: Eile, Axel Jonatan, kyrkoherde, Smålands Rydaholm, f. 17/4/87 i Bre-daryd, Jönköp. 1. G. 20 m. Ruth Lun-dell. Barn: Ingemar f. 21, Kerstin 23, Birgitta 26. — Mog:ex. i Lund 04, fil. kand. där 07, fil. ämb:ex. 14, teol. kand., prakt. teol. prov o. prästv. f. Växjö |Stift 17. Tjg. s. past:adj. i Jönköp. samt v. pastor i Bolm-sö, kommin. i Dannäs 20, kyrkoh. i Rydaholm sed. 39. Skr.: ett st. ant. art. i kul-turhist. m. fl. ämnen i ol. hemb :publ. samt tidn. o. tidskr. LVO.
translated: Eile, Axel Jonatan, clergyman, from Rydaholm in Småland, born on April 17, 1887 in Bre-daryd, Jönköping. 1st marriage in 1920 to Ruth Lundell. Children: Ingemar born in 1921, Kerstin in 1923, Birgitta in 1926. Divorced in Lund in 1904, passed Bachelor of Arts there in 1907, passed Bachelor of Philosophy in 1914, passed Bachelor of Theology and Practical Theology Exam and was ordained in Växjö Diocese in 1917. Served as assistant pastor in Jönköping, vice pastor in Bolmsö, curate in Dannäs in 1920, and parish priest in Rydaholm since 1939. Written one article on cultural history and several in other areas, published in various newspapers and magazines. Recipient of the Order of Vasa.
